				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\Delta {G}_{inj}$$\end{document}), open cycled voltage (VOC) and Gibbs free energy regeneration (ΔGreg\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
